<p class="ql-align-justify">面对疫情，资本比一般人更聪明、更警觉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201207/123fd444f48843bc8b7d0c036dd5199f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
